      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is priced to move and ready for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character and some needed repairs! While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and has seen better days, it's a great opportunity for a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves and bring some life back into a car with potential.",
