    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a solid daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the passenger side, and paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tire rotation. It\u2019s a honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
