    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership: the premium leather seating is free of cracks or stains, and the carpets have been protected by weather-proof mats since day one. All onboard electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has a complete service history showing regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake fluid flush. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with plenty of tread depth remaining, ensuring a smooth, vibration-free ride. This car has never been smoked in and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. It is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner. Inspections are welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
